nodes.text: I Have a Bad Feeling About This!

I Have a Bad Feeling About This! is an article written by Alex Newborn and published in Star Wars Insider 106. It discusses various details surrounding the production of The Star Wars Holiday Special, its influence on later Star Wars canon and its place in the history of the Star Wars franchise. This article was later reprinted in Star Wars Insider Special Edition 2012.
